text: Salah Ibrahim (born 1 July 1947) is a former Iraqi football midfielder who played for Iraq in the 1972 AFC Asian Cup. Salah played for the national team between 1971 and 1972. ==References== Category:Iraqi footballers Category:Iraq international footballers Category:1972 AFC Asian Cup players Category:Living people Category:Association football defenders Category:1947 births
